snippet.textDisplay:
Please don't let Disney destroy The New Mutants like they did with Dark Phoenix, I mean, an incomplete movie.
That speech " THE NEW MUTANTS WILL BE DIRECTOR'S ORIGINAL VERSION" is just marketing. A film that has already removed scenes isn't pure art, isn't an "ORIGINAL VERSION".
20th Century Fox disappointed me! I dislike Disney films, I don't know what to wait for after THE NEW MUTANTS. Maybe my time following Mutants is over, time to look for something different. FOX X-MEN, MUTANT SERIES were the best for me. I always wanted a 3rd Season for The Gifted but there wasn't a renew.
Thank you LAUREN, BRYAN, ALL THE PRODUCERS , ACTORS AND FILM CREW FOR THOSE AMAZING MOMENTS SINCE 2000.
I will always love the mutants!
Remember, Films and Comics are different arts.
20TH FOX end the FOX MUTANT UNIVERSE WITH SOMETHING EXCELLENT.
Bye!
